name: Windows 7 Shell Template
description:
This toolkit came from my need of Windows 7 UI resources, because as long as I had searched for them, I found nothing on Figma Community, so I took photos of official Windows 7 components and I tried to replicate then as faithfully as possible. I loved making this, since it wasn't hard, and I wanted to help a brother out by making this. I also wanted to help myself, in case I wanted to make more Aero concepts on Twitter, and I thank you for looking in here.


Any problems or suggestions? DM me on Discord at dlphin#7965! My Twitter is there at @dlphesigns too. G'day!
